01:40:38,115 --> 01:40:40,535
Two bullets in the back of his skull.

1053
01:40:40,618 --> 01:40:43,329
They found motor oil in his stomach.

1054
01:40:43,412 --> 01:40:45,373
Does that mean anything to you?

1055
01:40:45,456 --> 01:40:47,083
Wish I could help.

1056
01:40:47,166 --> 01:40:48,863
You'll be glad to know, I straightened

1057
01:40:48,864 --> 01:40:50,211
things out with the Americans.

1058
01:40:50,294 --> 01:40:52,171
Your friend Leiter's been promoted.

1059
01:40:52,255 --> 01:40:53,631
He replaced Beam.

1060
01:40:53,756 --> 01:40:56,175
Well, then the right
people kept their jobs.

1061
01:40:56,259 --> 01:40:58,010
Something like that.

1062
01:40:59,595 --> 01:41:02,098
Congratulations. You were right.

1063
01:41:02,181 --> 01:41:03,641
About what?

1064
01:41:04,183 --> 01:41:05,810
About Vesper.

1065
01:41:08,145 --> 01:41:09,480
Ma'am.

1066
01:41:11,816 --> 01:41:13,067
Bond,

1067
01:41:14,443 --> 01:41:16,153
I need you back.

1068
01:41:16,529 --> 01:41:18,030
I never left.

